example

example.py

A comprehensive tutorial demonstrating: - Computation of ISA 1983 atmospheric properties at selected altitudes - Derived quantities: dynamic pressure, Mach number, geometric height - Temperature offset handling - Proper plotting of atmospheric profiles up to 20 km
